#. <section class="sutta" id="sn13.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "1. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Tatiyapabbatasutta"
msgstr "11. A Mountain (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.139"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn13.11:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso sinerussa pabbatarājassa satta muggamattiyo "
"pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhipeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place down on Sineru, the king of "
"mountains, seven pebbles the size of mung beans."

msgctxt "sn13.11:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.11:1.4"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yā vā satta muggamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā "
"upanikkhittā yo vā sineru pabbatarājā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the seven pebbles the size of mung beans, or Sineru, the king "
"of mountains?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.11:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ yadidaṃ sineru pabbatarājā;"
msgstr "“Sir, Sineru, the king of mountains, is certainly more."

msgctxt "sn13.11:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta muggamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā."
msgstr "The seven pebbles the size of mung beans are tiny."

msgctxt "sn13.11:2.3"
msgid ""
"Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ "
"upenti sineruṃ pabbatarājānaṃ upanidhāya satta muggamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā "
"upanikkhittā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to Sineru, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred "
"thousandth part.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.11:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa "
"adhigamaṃ upanidhāya aññatitthiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇaparibbājakānaṃ adhigamo neva "
"satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, compared with the achievements of a noble disciple "
"accomplished in view, the achievements of the ascetics, brahmins, and "
"wanderers who follow other paths is not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or "
"a hundred thousandth part."

msgctxt "sn13.11:3.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ mahādhigamo, bhikkhave, diṭṭhisampanno puggalo, evaṃ mahābhiñño”ti."
msgstr ""
"So great is the achievement of the person accomplished in view, so great is "
"their direct knowledge.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.11:3.3"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn13.11:3.4"
msgid "Abhisamayasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on comprehension are complete."

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.11:4.1"
msgid "Nakhasikhā pokkharaṇī,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn13.11:4.2"
msgid "sambhejjaudake ca dve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn13.11:4.3"
msgid "Dve pathavī dve samuddā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn13.11:4.4"
msgid "tayo ca pabbatūpamāti."
msgstr ""
